fields.title: Update Dagger version to 1.2.1
fields.body:
Explicitly include Guava library, as it doesn't work as transitive
dependency, and bump it version to the newest released 17.0.

comment.text:
Tried to push it from develop branch, but it didn't work,
switching to master branch solved it:

```
(develop %>)$ pt propose -t "update-dagger" new
  To https://dev.gitblit.com/r/gitblit.git
! [remote rejected] HEAD -> refs/for/new%t=update-dagger (please squash to one commit)
```
